 2025-00722025-02-01FIN, GAC
ActCustoms Tariff
SubjectUnited States Surtax Order (2025)
PrecisUNITED STATES SURTAX ORDER (2025) in order to establish a 25% surtax on a range of goods imported from the United States, including consumer and household products such as certain food products, appliances, cosmetics and apparel; plastic products; and pulp and paper, covering a total of $30 billion in annual imports.
RegistrationRegistration: SOR/ 2025-0015 Publication Date: 2025-02-12
